{"ID":270124, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"124\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs123.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs125.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 124<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">world, nor of the devil, nor of his emissaries the dissenters, and those who love, and make, and\n  swear falsehoods,<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> to take away our lives.<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> We have never dissembled,<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> nor will we for the sake of\n  our lives.<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Forasmuch, then, as we know that we have been endeavoring with all our mind, might, and\n  strength,<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> to do the will of God,<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> and all things whatsoever He has commanded us;<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> and as to our\n  light speeches,<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> which may have escaped our lips from time to time, they have nothing to do with\n  the fixed purposes of our hearts; therefore it sufficeth us to say, that our souls were vexed from day\n  to day.<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> We refer you to Isaiah, who considers those who make a man an offender for a word, and\n  lay a snare for him that reproveth in the gate.<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> We believe that the old Prophet verily told the truth:\n  and we have no retraction to make. We have reproved in the gate, and men have laid snares for us.\n  We have spoken words, and men have made us offenders. And notwithstanding all this, our minds\n  are not yet darkened,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> but feel strong in the Lord.<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> But behold the words of the Savior: &ldquo;If the light\n  which is in you become darkness, behold how great is that darkness.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> Look at the dissenters.<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span>\n  Again, &ldquo;If you were of the world the world would love its own.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"wideEllipse\">* * *<\/p>\n\n  <div class=\"topic \">Blessed Are the Persecuted<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">Perhaps our brethren will say, because we thus write, that we are offended at these characters.\n  If we are, it is not for a word, neither because they reproved in the gate<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span>&mdash;but because they have\n  been the means of shedding innocent blood.<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> Are they not murderers then at heart?<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> Are not their\n  consciences seared as with a hot iron?<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> We confess that we are offended; but the Savior said, &ldquo;It\n  must needs be that offenses come, but woe unto them by whom they come.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span> And again, &ldquo;Blessed\n  are ye when men shall revile you, and persecute you, and shall say all manner of evil against you\n  falsely for my sake; rejoice and be exceeding glad, for great is your reward in heaven, for so\n  persecuted they the Prophets which were before you.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">21<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Now, dear brethren, if any men ever had reason to claim this promise,<span class=\"footRef\">22<\/span> we are the men; for we\n  know that the world not only hate us,<span class=\"footRef\">23<\/span> but they speak all manner of evil of us falsely,<span class=\"footRef\">24<\/span> for no other\n  reason than that we have been endeavoring to teach the fullness of the Gospel of Jesus Christ.<span class=\"footRef\">25<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107311\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107311)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107311)\">Jer. 5:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115753\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115753)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115753)\">D&amp;C 121:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117140\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117140)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117140)\">JS&mdash;H 1:61<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106460\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106460)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106460)\">1 Kgs. 19:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106680\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106680)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106680)\">Ps. 31:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110904\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110904)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110904)\">1 Ne. 1:20<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116953\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116953)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116953)\">Moses 8:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116979\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116979)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116979)\">Abr. 1:7,15,17,30<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106671\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106671)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106671)\">Ps. 26:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112924\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112924)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112924)\">Ether 15:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115202\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115202)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115202)\">D&amp;C 101:35<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113213\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113213)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113213)\">D&amp;C 11:20<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106550\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106550)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106550)\">Ezra 7:23<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107302\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107302)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107302)\">Jer. 1:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108293\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108293)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108293)\">Matt. 28:20<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108828\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108828)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108828)\">John 15:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111585\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111585)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111585)\">Mosiah 6:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115065\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115065)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115065)\">D&amp;C 94:10,12<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115110\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115110)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115110)\">D&amp;C 97:25-26<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116003\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116003)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116003)\">D&amp;C 124:55<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117048\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117048)\">&nbsp;<\/a>